questionsAndAnswers.question: How can I see your portfolio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have designed and developed hundreds of websites for my clients with 100% satisfaction. Please contact me for my detailed portfolio.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, all websites I create are responsive and look good on all devices.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do we can start working?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It is always best to leave me a message first so we can talk about the needs of your website. Everyone's project has different requirments and to avoid confusion, a brief conversation is highly recommended before your order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do I offer website hosting or domain registration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can help with domain registration, web hosting, and anything else regarding your website. Contact me for more information about this.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need from me to start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The requirements for the website include * A domain * A web hosting to host the website. * Content for each page on the website. * Logo files or color preferences for the brand if any. (optional) * Any images that you want to see on the website if you have some already.(optional)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is it easy to manage the website after itâ€™s developed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. WordPress is very user-friendly. I build websites with the end user in mind. You will be able to alter the website's text and images with ease. You'll even be able to add new pages if desired.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is there any hidden charge in your gig for some revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: no, there are no hidden charges for revisions in this gig.

questionsAndAnswers.question: May I have your personal contact information (email/skype or others) so that we can have better communication?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sorry, I can not provide my personal contact information as it is strictly prohibited in Fiverr and it is against the Fiverr TOS. Furthermore, I do not accept any job offer that goes against Fiverr TOS.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What kind of support can I expect after the delivery of my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Defects and bugs caused by me are always repaired free of charge no matter how long after completion. For one week you are more than welcome to ask me any questions and I will find a solution for you. Extended support is available in a 3-month package, please inquire with me directly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What happens if I lose my website  due to deletion of website by mistake?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I did not accept any responsibility for the delivered website. Also, I do not keep the backup of any delivered website. However, I can help you to restore your website from backup if provided by your hosting provider.
